---
import Card from "../layouts/Card.astro";
import ImageSection from "../layouts/ImageSection.astro";
import Page from "../layouts/Page.astro";
---

<Page title="Music">
  <section class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center my-10 mx-5">
    <Card
      className="flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-4 max-w-3xl border-gray-200 border border-opacity-40"
    >
      <img
        src="/images/the-emergent.jpg"
        alt="The Emergent"
        class="rounded-full w-36 h-36 md:w-48 md:h-48 mb-5 transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out"
      />
      <h1
        class="text-3xl md:text-4xl transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out font-bold mb-5 bg-gradient-to-tr from-pink-400 to-pink-200 bg-clip-text text-transparent"
      >
        The Emergent
      </h1>
      <p class="text-white text-lg lg:text-xl mb-5">
        Under <span class="font-bold italic">The Emergent</span>, I produce and
        release original songs and covers. My style is a mix of alternative and
        synth pop. I'm currently working on a new EP titled <span
          class="font-bold italic bg-gradient-to-tr from-purple-400 to-purple-200 bg-clip-text text-transparent"
          >All Over The Place</span
        > - a collection of songs from artists that inspired and taught me about
        different styles of music.
      </p>
    </Card>
    <section
      class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 items-center justify-center my-10 mx-5"
    >
      <iframe
        style="border-radius:12px"
        src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/track/08SoAk1UMG0VCQw6J42ZH4?utm_source=generator"
        width="100%"
        height="352"
        frameBorder="0"
        allowfullscreen=""
        allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture"
        loading="lazy"></iframe>
      <iframe
        style="border-radius:12px"
        src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/track/2AXpcGKEnyEZtaTeSG1InI?utm_source=generator"
        width="100%"
        height="352"
        frameBorder="0"
        allowfullscreen=""
        allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture"
        loading="lazy"></iframe>
    </section>
    <Card
      className="flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-4 max-w-3xl border-gray-200 border border-opacity-40"
    >
      <img
        src="/images/varun-vasudeva-music.jpg"
        alt="Music by Varun Vasudeva"
        class="rounded-full w-36 h-36 md:w-48 md:h-48 mb-5 transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out"
      />
      <h1
        class="text-3xl md:text-4xl transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out font-bold mb-5 bg-gradient-to-tr from-red-400 to-red-200 bg-clip-text text-transparent"
      >
        Varun Vasudeva
      </h1>
      <p class="text-white text-lg lg:text-xl mb-5">
        With a friend from high school (shoutout to <span
          class="font-bold italic bg-gradient-to-tr from-pink-400 to-pink-200 bg-clip-text text-transparent"
          >Karam</span
        >), I wrote and performed my first ever songs. They were equal parts
        music-making and learning experiences - it was the first time I had ever
        worked with a DAW and recorded vocals. The EP these songs were released
        under is titled <span
          class="font-bold italic bg-gradient-to-tr from-orange-400 to-orange-200 bg-clip-text text-transparent"
          >The Dark Room</span
        >. Have a listen below!
      </p>
    </Card>
    <section
      class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 items-center justify-center my-10 mx-5"
    >
      <iframe
        class="rounded-lg w-80 lg:w-96 h-72 lg:h-80 transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out"
        src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/IjcmVtCmrgE"
        title="YouTube video player"
        allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
        allowfullscreen></iframe>
      <iframe
        class="rounded-lg w-80 lg:w-96 h-72 lg:h-80 transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out"
        src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/APgxhr7A_84"
        title="YouTube video player"
        allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
        allowfullscreen></iframe>
      <iframe
        class="rounded-lg w-80 lg:w-96 h-72 lg:h-80 transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out"
        src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/N5jxCNMGR6Y"
        title="YouTube video player"
        frameborder="0"
        allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
        allowfullscreen></iframe>
    </section>
  </section>
</Page>
